{{refimprove|date=April 2017}}
'''Ngercheu''', or '''Carp Island''', is an island located within the nation of [[Palau]], specifically within the state of [[Peleliu]]. The island is located 5 km northwest of the main island of Peleliu. Ngercheu is roughly 1 sq km, star-shaped, and densely forested. The Carp Island Resort is located on the island and caters to an Asian tourist base.<ref>[https://www.hotelplanner.com/Hotels/159128/Reservations-Carp-Island-Resort-Palau-Diving-Center-Palau-Ngercheu-Island-96940 Carp Island Resort]</ref><ref>[https://mapcarta.com/27810312 MapCarta]</ref>

